<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>金竖琴不停地唱着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26491</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克偷偷看了看食人魔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32200</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他闭着眼睛在听歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32200</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34881</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，呼噜声响起，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34881</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>房子又跟着震动起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呼......呼......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咻......”食人魔的妻子叹了口气，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65412</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他终于睡着了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65412</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看到女人出去了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71611</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克心想：“就是现在！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71611</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从盆里跳出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他像只小老鼠，轻轻地走到桌子旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85256</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他抓起竖琴就跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克快速地跑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“主人呐！主人呐！”竖琴大声唱起来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“救救我！有小偷！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不！”杰克心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104390</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109214</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他紧紧地抓着竖琴，向大门跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109214</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“救救我！”竖琴又唱了起来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快醒醒，主人！有人要把我偷走了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133944</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔突然醒了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133944</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他愤怒地大吼一声，站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“站住，小偷！”食人魔大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他快速追了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149762</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是杰克已经跑出了大门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149762</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154673</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他继续快速往前跑！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154673</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157672</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔追了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你这个小偷！”他大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你跑不掉的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189762</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔一把抓起杰克！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189762</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是杰克挣脱了，他跑得更快了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“救救我，主人！”金竖琴还在唱着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212965</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克要快点儿跑到豆茎那里！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212965</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是食人魔就在他的身后！</Text>
